s="_ _8"></span>但他若不幸</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y24 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">离开了人间，我们也没什么好伤心的，佛法给了我们力量、</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y33 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls1c ws0">给了我们安慰。没有学佛的话，我们<span class="ls1d">这个家肯定早就崩溃</span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y34 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">了。<span class="_ _7"></span>”还有他的女儿，据说中观也学得很好。 </div><div class="t m0 x22 h4 y22c ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">在交谈的过程中，<span class="_ _6"></span>他们一直说说笑笑，<span class="_ _6"></span>特别坚强，<span class="_ _6"></span>我的</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y28 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">心却反而不忍，<span class="_ _6"></span>觉得他年纪轻轻的，<span class="_ _6"></span>实在太可怜了。<span class="_ _6"></span>但他因</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yd1 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">为有了佛法的引导，<span class="_ _d"></span><span class="ls16">在生离死别面前，<span class="_ _d"></span><span class="ls17">的确做到了非常坦然。<span class="_ _7"></span><span class="ls0"> </span></span></span></div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
